  "content": "<div style=\"max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px;\"><h1>Contributor Onboarding</h1><p>Follow this step-by-step guide to become an active contributor in the NeuroSwarm ecosystem.</p><h2>Step-by-Step Guide</h2><div style=\"margin-bottom: 2rem;\"><div style=\"background: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start;\"><div style=\"flex-shrink: 0;\"><div style=\"width: 3rem; height: 3rem; background: #dbeafe; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 1rem;\"><span style=\"color: #2563eb; font-size: 1.5rem;\">ğŸ’°</span></div></div><div style=\"flex: 1;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\"><span style=\"background: #f3f4f6; color: #374151; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; margin-right: 0.75rem;\">Step 1</span><h3 style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">Set Up Your Wallet</h3></div><p style=\"color: #374151; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\">Connect a Solana-compatible wallet to interact with the platform</p><p style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280;\">We recommend Phantom or Solflare wallets for the best experience.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"background: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start;\"><div style=\"flex-shrink: 0;\"><div style=\"width: 3rem; height: 3rem; background: #fef3c7; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 1rem;\"><span style=\"color: #d97706; font-size: 1.5rem;\">ğŸ†</span></div></div><div style=\"flex: 1;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\"><span style=\"background: #f3f4f6; color: #374151; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; margin-right: 0.75rem;\">Step 2</span><h3 style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">Earn Your First Badge</h3></div><p style=\"color: #374151; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\">Complete basic tasks to earn Bronze badge and voting rights</p><p style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280;\">Badges determine your voting power and access to governance features.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"background: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start;\"><div style=\"flex-shrink: 0;\"><div style=\"width: 3rem; height: 3rem; background: #d1fae5; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 1rem;\"><span style=\"color: #059669; font-size: 1.5rem;\">ğŸ“š</span></div></div><div style=\"flex: 1;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\"><span style=\"background: #f3f4f6; color: #374151; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; margin-right: 0.75rem;\">Step 3</span><h3 style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">Follow a Learning Path</h3></div><p style=\"color: #374151; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\">Choose a specialization and complete guided learning modules</p><p style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280;\">Paths include Developer, Validator, Community Manager, and Governance roles.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"background: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start;\"><div style=\"flex-shrink: 0;\"><div style=\"width: 3rem; height: 3rem; background: #e9d5ff; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 1rem;\"><span style=\"color: #7c3aed; font-size: 1.5rem;\">ğŸ‘¥</span></div></div><div style=\"flex: 1;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\"><span style=\"background: #f3f4f6; color: #374151; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; margin-right: 0.75rem;\">Step 4</span><h3 style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">Join a Working Group</h3></div><p style=\"color: #374151; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\">Contribute to active projects and collaborate with the community</p><p style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280;\">Working groups focus on specific areas like documentation, development, or outreach.</p></div></div></div></div><h2>Contributor Playbooks</h2><div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;\"><div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><h3 style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">Validator Playbook</h3><span style=\"padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; background: #fee2e2; color: #dc2626;\">Advanced</span></div><p style=\"color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Learn to run and maintain validator nodes</p><a href=\"https://getblockchain.tech/neuroswarm/portal\" style=\"color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;\">Read Playbook â†’</a></div><div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><h3 style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">Indexer Playbook</h3><span style=\"padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; background: #fef3c7; color: #d97706;\">Intermediate</span></div><p style=\"color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Build and maintain data indexing services</p><a href=\"https://getblockchain.tech/neuroswarm/portal\" style=\"color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;\">Read Playbook â†’</a></div><div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><h3 style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">Developer Playbook</h3><span style=\"padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; background: #fef3c7; color: #d97706;\">Intermediate</span></div><p style=\"color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Contribute code and technical improvements</p><a href=\"https://getblockchain.tech/neuroswarm/portal\" style=\"color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;\">Read Playbook â†’</a></div><div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><h3 style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">Governance Playbook</h3><span style=\"padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; background: #d1fae5; color: #059669;\">Beginner</span></div><p style=\"color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Master proposal creation and community governance</p><a href=\"https://getblockchain.tech/neuroswarm/portal\" style=\"color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;\">Read Playbook â†’</a></div></div><h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div style=\"margin-bottom: 2rem;\"><div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start;\"><span style=\"color: #2563eb; margin-right: 0.75rem; flex-shrink: 0;\">â“</span><div><h3 style=\"font-weight: 600; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\">How do I claim a badge?</h3><p style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Complete onboarding tasks and contribute to the platform. Badges are automatically awarded based on your activity and achievements.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start;\"><span style=\"color: #2563eb; margin-right: 0.75rem; flex-shrink: 0;\">â“</span><div><h3 style=\"font-weight: 600; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\">What's a learning path?</h3><p style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Learning paths are guided curricula that teach you specific skills needed for different contributor roles in NeuroSwarm.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start;\"><span style=\"color: #2563eb; margin-right: 0.75rem; flex-shrink: 0;\">â“</span><div><h3 style=\"font-weight: 600; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\">How do working groups work?</h3><p style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Working groups are focused teams tackling specific projects. Join based on your skills and interests to collaborate on meaningful work.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start;\"><span style=\"color: #2563eb; margin-right: 0.75rem; flex-shrink: 0;\">â“</span><div><h3 style=\"font-weight: 600; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\">What are the badge tiers?</h3><p style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Bronze (1 vote), Silver (3 votes), Gold (5 votes), and Diamond (10 votes). Higher tiers unlock more governance influence.</p></div></div></div></div><div style=\"background: linear-gradient(to right, #eff6ff, #f3e8ff); border: 1px solid #c7d2fe; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;\"><span style=\"color: #16a34a; font-size: 3rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">âœ…</span><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Ready to Start Your Journey?</h2><p style=\"color: #374151; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; max-width: 42rem; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">Join thousands of contributors building the future of decentralized AI. Your contributions help shape the platform and earn you governance rights.</p><div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;\"><a href=\"https://getblockchain.tech/neuroswarm/portal\" style=\"background: #2563eb; color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;\">Access Contributor Portal</a><a href=\"https://getblockchain.tech/neuroswarm/kb/governance\" style=\"background: #ffffff; color: #111827; padding: 0.75rem 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;\">Learn About Governance</a></div></div><h2>Continue Your Journey</h2><div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;\"><a href=\"https://getblockchain.tech/neuroswarm/kb/governance\" style=\"display: block; padding: 1.5rem; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;\"><span style=\"color: #7c3aed; font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">ğŸ—³ï¸</span><h3 style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\">Governance System</h3><p style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.875rem;\">Understand how your badges translate to voting power in governance decisions.</p></a><a href=\"https://getblockchain.tech/neuroswarm/kb/community\" style=\"display: block; padding: 1.5rem; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;\"><span style=\"color: #ea580c; font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">ğŸ’¬</span><h3 style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\">Community Resources</h3><p style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.875rem;\">Connect with other contributors and join working groups.</p></a><a href=\"https://getblockchain.tech/neuroswarm/kb/transparency\" style=\"display: block; padding: 1.5rem; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;\"><span style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">ğŸ“Š</span><h3 style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\">Transparency &amp; Logs</h3><p style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.875rem;\">Track your progress and see how governance decisions are made.</p></a></div></div>",
